"help_title": "Help",
"help_subtitle": "Frequently Asked Questions about MoveUP",

"help_q1_title": "Is MoveUP tracking me right now?",
"help_q2_title": "Does MoveUP work if the app is closed or the phone is locked?",
"help_q3_title": "Why do I need to allow location \"Always\"?",
"help_q4_title": "Does MoveUP consume a lot of battery?",
"help_q5_title": "Why do I sometimes see \"WAITING\"?",
"help_q6_title": "Does MoveUP track even when I am not moving?",
"help_q7_title": "Why do I see fewer data today compared to other days?",
"help_q8_title": "Can I stop or pause the tracking?",
"help_q9_title": "Are my data private?",
"help_q10_title": "What happens if I uninstall MoveUP?",

"help_q1_body": "If you see the LIVE or Listening status, MoveUP is monitoring your movement. The app can continue working even with the screen turned off.",
"help_q2_body": "Yes. MoveUP can continue tracking movement even when the app is not open, if you have granted location permission.",
"help_q3_body": "The \"Always\" permission allows MoveUP to work correctly even when you are not actively using the app, for example when the screen is off or when using other apps.",
"help_q4_body": "MoveUP uses GPS only when necessary and in an optimized way. Battery consumption mainly depends on how much you move during the day.",
"help_q5_body": "\"WAITING\" means that MoveUP is active but has not detected a new movement yet or is waiting for a stable GPS signal.",
"help_q6_body": "Yes. Periods of inactivity are also recorded. This helps MoveUP correctly understand how your day evolves.",
"help_q7_body": "This is normal. Data depend on your real movement during the day and the quality of the available GPS signal.",
"help_q8_body": "Yes. You can stop or pause tracking at any time from the main screen of the app.",
"help_q9_body": "Yes. Your movement data are personal and are used only for the features of the app.",
"help_q10_body": "If you uninstall MoveUP, tracking stops immediately. You can reinstall the app at any time.",

